rows.label: qst200716_0010
rows.name:
Mo mo, this is an amazing mushroom, mo!
Where on earth did you get it, mo?

rows.label: qst200716_0020
rows.name:
Is that dried-up mushroom
that amazing, mo?

rows.label: qst200716_0030
rows.name:
This is a Mashimashidake. If you soak it
in water, it will keep multiplying, mo.

rows.label: qst200716_0040
rows.name:
It went extinct over 100 years ago and was
said to be nowhere to be found, mo...

rows.label: qst200716_0050
rows.name:
I never dreamed I would see a
real one with my own eyes, mo...

rows.label: qst200716_0060
rows.name: It keeps growing-ppo?

rows.label: qst200716_0070
rows.name:
Yep, mo. To put it simply,
infinite mushrooms, mo.

rows.label: qst200716_0080
rows.name:
All-you-can-eat-ppo! I want you
to cook it right away-ppo!

rows.label: qst200716_0090
rows.name:
And serve it to everyone-ppo!
A grand mushroom party-ppo!

rows.label: qst200716_0100
rows.name:
You got it, mo! I'll
cook up a storm, mo.

rows.label: qst200716_0110
rows.name: Idaten is the best, mo!

rows.label: qst200716_0120
rows.name: So wonderful, mo!

rows.label: qst200716_0130
rows.name: Idaten, I'll call this match a draw-mau.

rows.label: qst200716_0140
rows.name:
This feeling of eating with the
Nopon... is quite nice-mau...

rows.label: qst200716_0150
rows.name:
I suppose I'll return all the
food I stole from you later-mau.

rows.label: qst200716_0160
rows.name:
So next time, let's have a
fair match, Maumau and I-mau.

rows.label: qst200716_0170
rows.name:
And we'll decide which of us is
more popular with the Nopon-mau.

rows.label: qst200716_0180
rows.name: Hey, are you listening-mau?

rows.label: qst200716_0190
rows.name:
Be quiet-ppo! Eat your food
quietly and deliciously-ppo.

rows.label: qst200716_0200
rows.name: Mauuuuu!
